{"type": "article", "id": 25645, "title": "Nendo 为意大利品牌De Padova 设计的家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-19T07:12:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125943wVULKkfr34n6p2SP.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是日本设计工作室 Nendo 为意大利品牌 De Padova 设计的灯和桌子，在极简设计中带有活泼的趣味。灯罩像是从一个鸟笼中“挖”开了一个洞，灯泡恰好固定在洞的中间，打破了原本规整的空间，非常生动。而茶几的底座是 11 块高低和大小不一的木块，上面是最普通的玻璃，就像是石头与河流的关系。木块是用柏木手工制作的，每一个都不一样，自然的纹路很有装饰性。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125940Tfjr6yGq2glzJbWu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70731707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125941hCTPIMNxoR1WA4QY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70609756\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125941FkeDL12r0q73iomn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70731707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125942BLDNzY56KrUSbaPt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70731707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125942cVxtd7ODiAfL5G0a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70609756\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}